capture photo (with servo position)
      hardware:servo, camera, 
      system:network connection,camera operating stuff
      api:take_photo(angle)
go forwards
      hardware:motors, motor controller, sensey thingy for proximity
      system:network connection code to make motors go
      api:move_motors(distance)
stop
      hardware:motors,motor controller
      system:network connection,code to make the motors stop
      api:Stop_motors()
      
go backwards
      hardware:motors, motor controller, sensey thingy for proximity
      system:network connection code to make motors go
      api:move_motors(distance)
turn left (degrees)
      hardware:motors, motor controller, sensey thingy for proximity
      system:network connection code to make motors go
      api:turn_servos(degrees)
turn right (degrees)
      hardware:motors, motor controller, sensey thingy for proximity
      system:network connection code to make motors go
      api:turn_servos(degrees)
